high_descs: Move across the room to the small, black stand with 3 shelves.
Pick up the tomato off of the stand.
Turn right and move to the long white rectangular table until you see two square pans on it.
Place the tomato in the pan that is on the right behind the green sponge.
Turn right and move to the end of the white table near the loaf of bread.
Pick up the large knife that is behind the loaf of bread.
Turn to the left and move back to the square pan with the tomato that is on the table.
Slice the tomato that is in the pan.
Put the knife in the same square pan with the tomato.
Pick up the pan with the tomato and knife in it.
Move to the counter that is to the left of the stove.
Place the pan with the tomato and knife in it on the counter on the left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Slice tomato to be placed in a pan with a knife to be moved to the counter by the stove.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the small black table
Grab the tomato off of the table
Turn right and stop at the left of the white table
Put the tomato on the pan on the table
Turn right and stop at the right of the white table
Grab the large knife off of the table
Move slightly to the left
Cut the tomato in the pan into slices
Put the knife in the pan
Grab the pan off of the table
Turn right and go to the counter to the left of the oven
Put the pan on the counter
anns.task_desc: Putting a pan with a knife and sliced tomato on a counter

high_descs: Look down, turn right, walk to door, turn right when you reach the door, walk straight to the small table.
Pick up the tomato on the table.
Look slightly up, turn right, walk straight to fridge and turn left to face the table with the knife on it.
Place the tomato on the pan on the table.
Turn right, walk straight, turn left to face the bread on the table and look down.
Pick up the small knife next to the bread on the table.
Look up slightly, turn left, walk straight, then turn right to face the tomato on the pan on the table.
Cut the tomato with the knife.
Place the knife on the pan next to the cut tomato.
Pick up the pan with the knife and tomato on it.
Turn around to face the table, then turn left to face the stove and walk straight to it.
Place the pan with the cut tomato and knife on it next to the counter next to the stove.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan with cut tomato on it and a knife on it on a counter.
